{"tid":1919942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"便衣與潮聯站長爭執 拉人後「掃場」","createTime":"2020-03-11T06:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T02:09:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":402,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":137,"replies":[{"pid":"5270043b7537a4245b50fa9b636bc1a46ef528f9","tid":1919942,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:27:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200311/7RENX2CCTR2KZO54KG6GT7YILI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200311%2F7RENX2CCTR2KZO54KG6GT7YILI%2F&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=59d7c4b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200311%2F7RENX2CCTR2KZO54KG6GT7YILI%2F&h=caf7d4d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200311/7RENX2CCTR2KZO54KG6GT7YILI/</a><br />\n<br />\n便衣與潮聯站長爭執 拉人後「掃場」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一向鮮明撐警的「潮聯」小巴，旺角站頭昨罕有發生站長與便衣警爭執場面。數名便衣警員駕駛私家車停泊於通菜街潮聯小巴站頭後，與站長發生爭執口角，站長聲稱：「佢哋（警方）話要搞到潮聯站頭郁唔到，掃晒所有車」，他未幾被帶返警署調查。其後，十多名警員到來「掃場」，向違泊小巴發出告票。有網民指，過往多次投訴潮聯小巴違泊警方都未有行動，質疑是否選擇性執法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200311/large/1583858572_ebf1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200311%2Flarge%2F1583858572_ebf1.gif&h=4679951c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名便衣警與潮聯站長口角，更捉住對方左手。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警疑駕車泊站頭<br />\n<br />\n目擊者表示，昨晚7時許，3男1女便衣警員駕駛一輛私家車，泊於通菜街慢線潮聯小巴站頭，小巴站長勸喻對方駛離時，雙方發生口角。從現場拍攝的短片所見，坐在椅上的站長高舉雙手叫救命，其左手被一名男便衣捉住，站長高呼「同我錄低佢，佢捉住我隻手話我攻擊佢！」其間便衣警要求他冷靜及出示身份證，站長卻大聲叫喊：「佢話要搞到潮聯車站郁唔到，掃晒所有車！」由於在鬧巿街頭，吸引大批巿民圍觀，事件大約擾攘10分鐘。現場消息稱，站長最終被指阻差辦公及行為不檢，被帶回警署。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200311/large/1583858571_e239.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200311%2Flarge%2F1583858571_e239.jpg&h=c055e15e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多名交通警到場抄牌「掃場」。司徒韋桐攝<br />\n<br />\n至晚上9時半，10名軍裝警連同5名交通警，以及7名交通督導員到現場執勤，至少向一輛違泊小巴發告票。本報向警方查問事件，至截稿前未獲回應。<br />\n<br />\n2014年雨傘革命期間，潮聯小巴曾高調撐警，更聲稱因佔領事件蒙受損失，申請旺角臨時禁制令，並獲警方協助清場。"},{"pid":"f5cab8c0cfdca6214719286c62309bfcf6b59257","tid":1919942,"uid":85327,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adf915411c538eb466b8c75ec55d7600f9a3c455","tid":1919942,"uid":89869,"like":215,"dislike":1,"score":214,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:28:21.000Z","msg":"一定係小巴收撚左錢搞三搞四"},{"pid":"42b369d165f161aab4805e883f4ffe2383561f4b","tid":1919942,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee31672651b8ce27e194e9e82e7d7d90b40e935d","tid":1919942,"uid":156652,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:28:47.000Z","msg":"因果"},{"pid":"eeb8b7b3bd4fecd210a74f6264593f7a9ea09855","tid":1919942,"uid":70786,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"港共開始收割<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b248e70c5175f7c384824b114dec2708a9932b1","tid":1919942,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b889cbdbca822b96af4aa8b573381e2ae6b877e","tid":1919942,"uid":192215,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:30:44.000Z","msg":"竟然敢得罪特權份子??<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedb85617c11bf3ee9a4febef44bb04c080e0cb1","tid":1919942,"uid":224066,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":