"d3ca1dab49b565f0146019d2ab35428c46237b24","tid":1919942,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:07:32.000Z","msg":"支持警察嚴正執法👮"},{"pid":"b8642d6ed110f9dd0a8995c9aed81db300a69d92","tid":1919942,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:09:36.000Z","msg":"黑警已成特權貴族 邊個都唔洗比面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4cfcf81362a94a633356cb3354db2a09aed8133","tid":1919942,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:10:27.000Z","msg":"根本一早要清算潮聯，死黑警幾廿年都唔做嘢"},{"pid":"60c6be23601ce55bfc97982c527daa5a370927cd","tid":1919942,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"745ff4c6d2e225944434ba17471aa90cb7594584","tid":1919942,"uid":272569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5270043b7537a4245b50fa9b636bc1a46ef528f9","tid":1919942,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:27:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200311/7RENX2CCTR2KZO54KG6GT7YILI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200311%2F7RENX2CCTR2KZO54KG6GT7YILI%2F&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=59d7c4b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200311%2F7RENX2CCTR2KZO54KG6GT7YILI%2F&h=caf7d4d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200311/7RENX2CCTR2KZO54KG6GT7YILI/</a><br />\n<br />\n便衣與潮聯站長爭執 拉人後「掃場」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一向鮮明撐警的「潮聯」小巴，旺角站頭昨罕有發生站長與便衣警爭執場面。數名便衣警員駕駛私家車停泊於通菜街潮聯小巴站頭後，與站長發生爭執口角，站長聲稱：「佢哋（警方）話要搞到潮聯站頭郁唔到，掃晒所有車」，他未幾被帶返警署調查。其後，十多名警員到來「掃場」，向違泊小巴發出告票。有網民指，過往多次投訴潮聯小巴違泊警方都未有行動，質疑是否選擇性執法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200311/large/1583858572_ebf1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200311%2Flarge%2F1583858572_ebf1.gif&h=4679951c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名便衣警與潮聯站長口角，更捉住對方左手。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警疑駕車泊站頭<br />\n<br />\n目擊者表示，昨晚7時許，3男1女便衣警員駕駛一輛私家車，泊於通菜街慢線潮聯小巴站頭，小巴站長勸喻對方駛離時，雙方發生口角。從現場拍攝的短片所見，坐在椅上的站長高舉雙手叫救命，其左手被一名男便衣捉住，站長高呼「同我錄低佢，佢捉住我隻手話我攻擊佢！」其間便衣警要求他冷靜及出示身份證，站長卻大聲叫喊：「佢話要搞到潮聯車站郁唔到，掃晒所有車！」由於在鬧巿街頭，吸引大批巿民圍觀，事件大約擾攘10分鐘。現場消息稱，站長最終被指阻差辦公及行為不檢，被帶回警署。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200311/large/1583858571_e239.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200311%2Flarge%2F1583858571_e239.jpg&h=c055e15e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多名交通警到場抄牌「掃場」。司徒韋桐攝<br />\n<br />\n至晚上9時半，10名軍裝警連同5名交通警，以及7名交通督導員到現場執勤，至少向一輛違泊小巴發告票。本報向警方查問事件，至截稿前未獲回應。<br />\n<br />\n2014年雨傘革命期間，潮聯小巴曾高調撐警，更聲稱因佔領事件蒙受損失，申請旺角臨時禁制令，並獲警方協助清場。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:19:31.000Z","msg":"警甴攪鳩自己啲黑社會上司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:11:04.000Z","msg":"dllm 止暴制亂緊架咪打擊士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a2a650c36ae50a8fc591338312ee97c642ad2e","tid":1919942,"uid":22088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"潮聯唔係驚呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一縮就一世"},{"pid":"8f8bc408f9480abb1dbd6684f7a4934e35deac3f","tid":1919942,"uid":268429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:13:34.000Z","msg":"支持警察嚴正執法👮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5777050a3a5aceed96781a49fa1f545f1412f6e1","tid":1919942,"uid":