d743b6355ce1","tid":1919942,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:58:56.000Z","msg":"呢D咪又係搵分區指揮官同D大佬傾下就了事"},{"pid":"969d3c6a3a1b83a66e0fdd2f8b01f0a883f823b6","tid":1919942,"uid":141286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5270043b7537a4245b50fa9b636bc1a46ef528f9","tid":1919942,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:27:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200311/7RENX2CCTR2KZO54KG6GT7YILI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200311%2F7RENX2CCTR2KZO54KG6GT7YILI%2F&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=59d7c4b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200311%2F7RENX2CCTR2KZO54KG6GT7YILI%2F&h=caf7d4d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200311/7RENX2CCTR2KZO54KG6GT7YILI/</a><br />\n<br />\n便衣與潮聯站長爭執 拉人後「掃場」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一向鮮明撐警的「潮聯」小巴，旺角站頭昨罕有發生站長與便衣警爭執場面。數名便衣警員駕駛私家車停泊於通菜街潮聯小巴站頭後，與站長發生爭執口角，站長聲稱：「佢哋（警方）話要搞到潮聯站頭郁唔到，掃晒所有車」，他未幾被帶返警署調查。其後，十多名警員到來「掃場」，向違泊小巴發出告票。有網民指，過往多次投訴潮聯小巴違泊警方都未有行動，質疑是否選擇性執法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200311/large/1583858572_ebf1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200311%2Flarge%2F1583858572_ebf1.gif&h=4679951c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名便衣警與潮聯站長口角，更捉住對方左手。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警疑駕車泊站頭<br />\n<br />\n目擊者表示，昨晚7時許，3男1女便衣警員駕駛一輛私家車，泊於通菜街慢線潮聯小巴站頭，小巴站長勸喻對方駛離時，雙方發生口角。從現場拍攝的短片所見，坐在椅上的站長高舉雙手叫救命，其左手被一名男便衣捉住，站長高呼「同我錄低佢，佢捉住我隻手話我攻擊佢！」其間便衣警要求他冷靜及出示身份證，站長卻大聲叫喊：「佢話要搞到潮聯車站郁唔到，掃晒所有車！」由於在鬧巿街頭，吸引大批巿民圍觀，事件大約擾攘10分鐘。現場消息稱，站長最終被指阻差辦公及行為不檢，被帶回警署。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200311/large/1583858571_e239.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200311%2Flarge%2F1583858571_e239.jpg&h=c055e15e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多名交通警到場抄牌「掃場」。司徒韋桐攝<br />\n<br />\n至晚上9時半，10名軍裝警連同5名交通警，以及7名交通督導員到現場執勤，至少向一輛違泊小巴發告票。本報向警方查問事件，至截稿前未獲回應。<br />\n<br />\n2014年雨傘革命期間，潮聯小巴曾高調撐警，更聲稱因佔領事件蒙受損失，申請旺角臨時禁制令，並獲警方協助清場。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:59:15.000Z","msg":"至晚上9時半，10名軍裝警連同5名交通警，以及7名交通督導員到現場執勤，至少向<span style=\"color: red;\">一輛</span>違泊小巴發告票。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">只要在2020年7月25日或以前年滿18歲，今年5月2日前可登記做選民\n\n18歲生日快樂 即刻登記做選民</code></pre><br />\n選民登記填表機<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=3cc69873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote</a><br />\n地方選區選民新登記申請表：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=29c8aaf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n選民資料網上查閱系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=33f465db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/M8STBFS.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/a8T7y6C.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"5b61897a412d21f9d56deac6509f8cfdeac13ce6","tid":1919942,"uid":169116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:59:38.000Z","msg":"黑吃黑"},{"pid":"1d4a08d6baf0980b7187581e2d3cd0b56cf19bf5","tid":1919942,"uid":29014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2